02-25T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"雙魚人<br />\n覺得自己有d雙面<br />\n喺人面前會好樂觀<br />\n自己一個好易諗埋d唔開心野<br />\n追求刺激<br />\n感性"},{"pid":"b4945fa59d78179143218057a4b95fd838b6e5d0","tid":133643,"uid":65798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔鐘意雙魚座嘅人無目標，無計劃，無鬥志，<br />\n日日好似發夢咁，想一巴星過去！</blockquote><br />\n其實又唔可以話無目標嘅，雙魚如我如果自己被需要時會訓身盡力做好自己，甚至更多"},{"pid":"a2967883cc49cec82e90ed87e6d4296531464fa8","tid":133643,"uid":65798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T19:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雙魚人<br />\n覺得自己有d雙面<br />\n喺人面前會好樂觀<br />\n自己一個好易諗埋d唔開心野<br />\n追求刺激<br />\n感性</blockquote><br />\n會唔會覺得負面野係自己不可分割嘅一部分先，我自己有時覺得咁係一種浪漫，但知道過多會沉淪"},{"pid":"6255deb40b58e296dca1411906d160c3d20b77cb","tid":133643,"uid":76578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2ew4ma9i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2ew4ma9i&h=e5bd5f20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0b61e14014e878e28d6e3693bf49efda8e0b3ad","tid":133643,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"隻魚同蛇夫夾唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855c925c2a5513e376e7d127207328316b96a66b","tid":133643,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雙魚同蛇夫夾唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9556b4db6bcb198afe0f0fe6bcb034ad6911685b","tid":133643,"uid":65798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T03:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻魚同蛇夫夾唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb0cc585b4794589b6e1ff2eeee304d49988df2","tid":133643,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-